{"tid":1696872,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發) 何君堯內出血要做手術及留院","createTime":"2019-11-06T12:36:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T12:46:05.000Z","uid":173889,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"87d6858ef95b1e073a19cdba72125f7e4bee9ff5","tid":1696872,"uid":173889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T12:36:19.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】立法會議員何君堯的哥哥到醫院探望何君堯，他表示何君堯內出血要做手術，暫時要留院，又透露因應近日社會氣氛，何君堯有聘請保鑣人員，保障自身安全。<br />\n<br />\n何君柱（何君堯哥哥）：「（何君堯）今日的事情大家都可能有感覺，有預料可能會發生，所以有聘請保鑣；警察我相信有，但這些突襲很難防止。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E5%85%84-%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E5%85%A7%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%80%E8%A6%81%E5%81%9A%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E5%8F%8A%E7%95%99%E9%99%A2-081732941.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF%25E5%2585%2584-%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25A1%2580%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%2581%259A%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25A1%2593%25E5%258F%258A%25E7%2595%2599%25E9%2599%25A2-081732941.html&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX2jFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=38cff59c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E5%85%84-%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E5%85%A7%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%80%E8%A6%81%E5%81%9A%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E5%8F%8A%E7%95%99%E9%99%A2-081732941.html</a>"},{"pid":"d088b122958280be70d11a1fc82f8aa36ecc38aa","tid":1696872,"uid":250511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T12:37:48.000Z","msg":"微絲血管爆裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7957b3f6c82aa3502b9e6c6fda24b7cd0b239445","tid":1696872,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r